commits.author: Shai Erera
commits.sourceNew:
/** * Initializes a new instance with the given dimension-to-params mapping. The * dimension is considered as what's returned by * {@link CategoryPath#components cp.components[0]}. * *

* NOTE: for any dimension whose {@link CategoryListParams} is not * defined in the mapping, a default {@link CategoryListParams} will be used. * * @see #PerDimensionIndexingParams(Map, CategoryListParams) */ public PerDimensionIndexingParams(Map paramsMap) { this(paramsMap, DEFAULT_CATEGORY_LIST_PARAMS); }
